gment and merge, verify the merged summary is coherent (no contradictions), contains all key decisions and action items, and loses no critical information.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":"An Integration test with mocked LLM could verify splitting and sequential structure, but would not catch incoherent merges or information loss that the real LLM produces.","level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.05,"Integration":0.15,"System":0.05,"Agentic":0.7,"Workflow":0.05}},{"behavior_id":5,"description":"Full pipeline completes end-to-end without manual intervention for a real meeting recording","minimum_level":"Agentic","justification":"The full pipeline chains real speech-to-text API (System) and real LLM summarization (Agentic). The LLM step is the binding constraint because mocking it would hide failures in the real model's ability to produce valid structured output. While the speech-to-text API call is a System dependency, the agentic step (LLM correctness) determines whether the output is actually useful.","test_description":"Upload a real meeting recording (or high-fidelity test recording), run the complete pipeline with real speech-to-text API and real LLM, verify structured output (action items, decisions, attendee attributions) is delivered, contains no errors, and requires zero manual corrections.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":"A System-level test with a real speech-to-text API but mocked LLM would not catch failures where the real LLM produces malformed or incomplete structured output.","level_probabilities":{"Unit":0,"Integration":0.05,"System":0.05,"Agentic":0.85,"Workflow":0.05}}]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13361,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":13361},"output_tokens":5,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_u